            <title>[LU-3323] Support for restricting connections to ksocklnd and ko2iblnd for permitted NIDs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3323</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add support to lnet for a permitted_nids parameter which can be set similar to the root squash settings and restrict connections to external systems similar to TCP wrappers.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will upload a patch when I finish making the changes to it for the 2.4 code.  Currently it will only be implemented for ksocklnd and ko2iblnd.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
